AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Nancy F. Atlas: Judge in the case of Jose Marlon Ibarra-Zelaya
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.Jose Marlon Ibarra-Zelaya: Defendant who filed a motion to vacate, set aside, or correct sentence and charged with conspiracy and assorted offenses related to an illegal alien smuggling venture
AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.United States Federal Grand Jury: Returned a five-count superseding indictment against Jose Marlon Ibarra-Zelaya and co-defendants for conspiracy and offenses stemming from an illegal alien smuggling venture
